    "body": "Hello @foufrix 👋\r\n\r\nHave you tried to use the connectors API https://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/v2/guides/customization.html ?\r\n\r\nI've built recently components for [etch](https://github.com/atom/etch) (which is yet another framework for building webpages) using the connectors API and it was pretty straightforward 👍 \r\n\r\nIf not or if it doesn't fit your needs, I'll find some time to try Angular v4 and provide an example on how to use it with InstantSearch.js\r\n\r\nCheers, Max.",
